name: podamShouldHandleConstructorsWithMultipleGenericsDuringPojoInstantiation

testSteps.description: When I invoke Podam for a Generic Pojo specifying the concrete types
Then the Object should not be null
Then the two objects class java.lang.String and class java.lang.String should be equal
Then the collection should not be null or empty and each element should be of type G
Then the Map should not be null or empty and each element should have key of type 102=-1932633882 and value of type 120=-1071242465

title: Podam should handle constructors with multiple generics during Pojo instantiation
